  "text": "Ears were immersed in mRNAlater solution (Applied Biosystems) and kept at ¯Ç▓80┬░C, and then homogenized using Tissue Lyser II (QIAGEN) and total mRNA was purified using the Fibrous Mini kit (QIAGEN). After reverse transcription into cDNA using the Reverse Transcription kit (QIAGEN), PCR was performed on a Viia7 RT-PCR detection system (Applied Biosystems). Full-length versus ¯üätm Il15ra mRNA was assessed using RT-PCR, whereas levels of all other cytokines were determined via quantitative RT-PCR using SYBR Green supermix (QIAGEN). The sequences of specific primers (from Microsynth) were as follows: Il15 forward, 5¯Ç╣-CATCCATCTCGTGCTACTTGTG-3¯Ç╣; Il15 reverse, 5¯Ç╣-GCCTCT-GTTTTAGGGAGACCT-3¯Ç╣; full-length Il15ra forward, 5¯Ç╣-ATGGCCT-CGCCGCAG-3¯Ç╣; full-length Il15ra reverse, 5¯Ç╣-TTAGGCTCCTGT-GTCTTCATC-3¯Ç╣; ¯üätm Il15ra forward, 5¯Ç╣-ATGGCCTCGCCGCAG-3¯Ç╣; ¯üätm Il15ra reverse, 5¯Ç╣-GGACTTGTGACTGCCTGTCC-3¯Ç╣; Il17 forward, 5¯Ç╣-TTGGAGGCAGACACCCACC-3¯Ç╣; Il17 reverse, 5¯Ç╣-GATAGCGGTCC-TCATCCGTG-3¯Ç╣; Il22 forward, 5¯Ç╣-ATACATCGTCAACCGCACCTTT-3¯Ç╣; Il22 reverse, 5¯Ç╣-AGCCGGACATCTGTGTTGTTAT-3¯Ç╣; Il23p19 forward, 5¯Ç╣-TATCCAGTGTGAAGATGGTTGTG-3¯Ç╣; Il23p19 reverse, 5¯Ç╣-CACTA-AGGGCTCAGTCAGAGTTG-3¯Ç╣; Tnfa forward, 5¯Ç╣-TGTAGCCCACGT-CGTAGCAAA-3¯Ç╣; Tnfa reverse, 5¯Ç╣-CTGGCACCACTAGTTGGTTGT-3¯Ç╣. Gene expression was normalized using the ribosomal protein L27 (RPL27) housekeeping gene and data are represented as fold differences by the 2 ¯Ç▓¯üä¯üäCt method, with ¯üäCt = Ct target gene ¯Ç▓ Ct Rpl27 , and ¯üä¯üäCt = ¯üäCt induced ¯Ç▓ ¯üäCt reference , as previously published [CITATION_1] .",
